lee-1851282635\">Read more...</a></p>", "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/tekken-8-ai-ghost-katsuhiro-harada-kohei-ikeda-lee-1851282635", "age": null, "source_obj__id": 492, "album": "", "page_rating_contents": 0, "page_rating_visits": 0, "permanent": false, "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "page_rating_votes": 0, "page_rating": 0, "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/79697e9013db37479a91301c62bcc3d3.jpg", "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss"}, {"tags": [], "user": null, "title": "It\u2019s Time For Game Devs To Kill The Killmonger Swoop", "vote": 0, "date_published": "2024-02-23T20:00:00+00:00", "dead": false, "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/09c24fccf88f1444909810492afeac71.jpg\" /><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/prince-of-persia-lost-crown-tekken-8-killmonger-hair-1851282520\">Read more...</a></p>", "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/prince-of-persia-lost-crown-tekken-8-killmonger-hair-1851282520", "age": null, "source_obj__id": 492, "album": "", "page_rating_contents": 0, "page_rating_visits": 0, "permanent": false, "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "page_rating_votes": 0, "page_rating": 0, "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/09c24fccf88f1444909810492afeac71.jpg", "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss"}, {"tags": [], "user": null, "title": "Helldivers 2 Is Committed To The Bit And So Are We", "vote": 0, "date_published": "2024-02-23T19:45:00+00:00", "dead": false, "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/f52b300d8fbacb34dddae721741d6f43.jpg\" /><p>I haven\u2019t had the chance to play much of <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/helldivers-2-kotaku-review-pc-ps5-is-it-good-ps-plus-1851258251\">Helldivers 2</a>. At first, <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-