"language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/ones-who-live-walking-dead-review-1851282516", "age": null, "source_obj__id": 492, "album": "", "page_rating_contents": 0, "page_rating_visits": 0, "permanent": false, "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "page_rating_votes": 0, "page_rating": 0, "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/a12de2ac405fad312706322a230f6c60.jpg", "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss"}, {"tags": [], "user": null, "title": "PlayStation Plus Just Added 2022\u2019s Most Stylish Arcade Racer", "vote": 0, "date_published": "2024-02-23T19:15:00+00:00", "dead": false, "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/ee2e3a46e897addb0fe6f0bed4d5c138.jpg\" /><p>Driving games can loosely be divided into two sub-genres: simulation and arcade. The former category includes the likes of <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/gran-turismo-7-polyphony-digital-ps5-balance-rewards-up-1848766803\">Gran Turismo</a> or <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/forza-motorsport-8-horizon-xbox-game-pass-review-120fps-1850900323\">Forza</a> (not the <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/forza-horizon-5-the-kotaku-review-1847989847\">Horizon</a> series) and focus on more realistic racing. But the latter is all about fun over realism. 2022\u2019s <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/need-for-speed-unbound-review-anime-forza-gran-turismo-1849842594\">N", "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/need-for-speed-unbound-playstation-plus-1851282455", "age": null, "source_obj__id": 492, "album": "", "page_rating_contents": 0, "page_rating_visits": 0, "permanent": false, "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "page_rating_votes": 0, "page_rating": 0, "thumbnail": "https: