load/c_fit,q_80,w_636/6ea51c7ace2405d322667fda9baf1ee2.jpg\" /><p>In the summer of 2020, as America tried to reckon with its institutionalized racism, the Black Lives Matter movement prompted <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/game-companies-say-they-re-supporting-black-lives-matte-1843882888\">video game studios to issue pro-BLM statements</a>, donate to Black-centered charities, and promise to elevate Black voices. Several years later, it\u2019s not all that clear if some (or any) studios <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://www.pcgamer.com/has-the-games-industry-lived-up-to-its-black-lives-matter-promises/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">fol\u2026</a></p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/tales-of-kenzera-zau-abubakar-salim-interview-1851279758\">Read more...</a></p>", "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/tales-of-kenzera-zau-abubakar-salim-interview-1851279758", "age": null, "source_obj__id": 492, "album": "", "page_rating_contents": 0, "page_rating_visits": 0, "permanent": false, "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "page_rating_votes": 0, "page_rating": 0, "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/6ea51c7ace2405d322667fda9baf1ee2.jpg", "source": "https://kotaku.com/rss"}, {"tags": [], "user": null, "title": "Genshin Impact\u2019s Lantern Rite Festival Is A Heartfelt Homage To The Game\u2019s Roots", "vote": 0, "date_published": "2024-02-23T15:00:00+00:00", "dead": false, "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/cd0cf614f551a963679d7dedc974bafa.jpg\" /><p>This year, I returned to <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/a-farewell-to-liyue-an-exceptional-part-of-genshin-imp-1846093827\">Liyue Harbor</a> to find paper kites flying alongside strings of vermillion lanterns. I couldn\u2019t help but r